(42, 'ppxo-pps-upgrade-paypal-payments-2', 'info', 'en_US', 'Upgrade your PayPal experience!', 'We\'ve developed a whole new <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-paypal-payments/\" target=\"_blank\">PayPal extension for WooCommerce</a> that combines the best features of our many PayPal extensions into just one extension.<br /><br />Get access to a full suite of PayPal payment methods, extensive currency and country coverage, offer subscription and recurring payments, and the new PayPal pay later options.<br /><br />Start using our latest PayPal today to continue to receive support and updates.', '{}', 'pending', 'woocommerce.com', '2021-06-27 15:55:31', NULL, 0, 'plain', '', 0, 'info');

